name: Chinese dragon
description: Dragon is a supernatural animal in ancient Chinese legend. Dragon is one of the most representative traditional cultures of the Han nationality. Other Asian countries and nationalities are also influenced by Chinese dragon culture.  Most of the legends are that it can show and hide, it can be fine, it can be huge, it can be short and it can be long. Spring equinox in the sky, autumn equinox in the abyss, call the wind and call the rain
